      "content": "i hear you on the wealth gap part, but as a business owner i'm more concerned with my specific bottom line right now. it feels like you're saying the \"fairness\" of the wage is more important than whether or not my business actually survives the transition. so if i'm being honest, i'm not really looking for a lecture on sociology, i need to know if there's any actual economic evidence that shows these hikes don't hurt small businesses in the long run. or is it just a matter of \"doing the right thing\" regardless of the cost?",
